snippet: The government will lease six levels of the 104-story 1 World Trade Center.
abstract: Federal government announces plans to become the third tenant at 1 World Trade Center, occupying six floors of the new 104-story building in a 20-year lease; announcement means that more than half of the space inside the fast-rising tower has now been leased.
lead_paragraph: The government will lease six levels of the 104-story 1 World Trade Center.

headline.seo: Federal Government Signs Lease for 1 World Trade Center
headline.main: Federal Government Agrees to Occupy Six Floors at New Trade Tower
headline.print_headline: Federal Government Agrees to Occupy Six Floors at New Trade Tower
